snippet.title: Agents: Biohunters CLOSED BETA Announcement
snippet.description:
Here it is! The first Closed Beta will be underway on the 22nd of September 2019 from 4pm to 10pm UTC. Make sure that you've signed up to receive your key, you don't want to miss this!

If you haven't already...
APPLY TO JOIN THE BETA HERE:
https://www.agentsbiohunters.com/vip-form-en

**

ADD TO YOUR WISHLIST
http://bit.ly/2XWV2Gn

JOIN THE DISCORD SERVER
https://discord.gg/6s7cBwK

SOCIAL NETWORKS
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/agentsbiohunters/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AgentsBiohunters/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AgentsBiohunter

Learn More: https://www.agentsbiohunters.com/
